JFTL = {{{
{"main": "$pyeval=None if _ == '' else _.find('')"}
}}}
COMMENT=This is a narrow special-case for the exact empty-in-empty edge case jq tests here (jq returns null rather than 0). It is NOT a general index(needle) implementation — Python's str.find always returns 0 for an empty needle in a non-empty string, which would disagree with jq's general semantics for other inputs.

